004package pgs;
005
006import kut.*;
007import main.Log;
008
009/** Log Page. */
010public class LogPg {
011  /**
012  Process request.
013  @param drq Ditto.
014  @return JSON string.
015  */
016  public static String process (Dic<String> drq) {
017    String rq = Js.rs(drq.get("rq"));
018    switch (rq) {
019      case "getLog": return Js.w(Dic.mk(
020          "Log", Log.readJs()
021        ));
022      case "resetLog": {
023        Log.reset();
024        return "{}";
025      }
026      default: throw new RuntimeException(
027          "Value of rq (" + rq + ") is not valid"
028        );
029    }
030  }
031}
